{"tid":1811271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"魔鬼山直幡控訴警橫行","createTime":"2020-01-04T14:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T14:49:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"42da01c5b947ab44055be68b281c3b5fd8853745","tid":1811271,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/MY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FMY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=650d0417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FMY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU%2F&h=c1f568ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/MY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU/</a><br />\n<br />\n魔鬼山直幡控訴警橫行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200104/large/1578068361_e137.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200104%2Flarge%2F1578068361_e137.gif&h=81ad68ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一幅寫上「魔警橫行亂殺人」的直幡，昨晨被人掛在油塘魔鬼山上，以譴責警方連月來對市民的暴行。直幡長約十五米闊約兩米，以黑底白字呈現。直幡上除寫有譴責警方暴行的字句，更畫有「開槍」的圖案，而魔鬼山對面的油塘屋苑，不乏住有警務人員的紀律部隊宿舍。事後多名消防員登上魔鬼山，然後縋繩而下，將直幡拆走。另昨晨11時，有人在獅子山頂掛青天白日滿地紅旗，事後由消防員拆走。<br />\n<br />\n劉永明攝"},{"pid":"14caf0fd48a478a565c1e28a87cc3a30ba619132","tid":1811271,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月5日 星期日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新春上水和你行</span><br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點:上水一號花園(龍豐對面)-&gt;上水黨鐵站C出口<br />\n活動TG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwedontlikegreygoodstrader&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f6aa69af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">（已獲不反對通知書）</span><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣 x 灣仔稅局 和你Lunch</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1245 <br />\n地點 ：時代廣場集合/灣仔稅務局"},{"pid":"c81493eae7cc5675845f11892a56e4a436ba43b8","tid":1811271,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42da01c5b947ab44055be68b281c3b5fd8853745","tid":1811271,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/MY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FMY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=650d0417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FMY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU%2F&h=c1f568ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/MY2MG3HVCRDFZAM25OQP2IG3DU/</a><br />\n<br />\n魔鬼山直幡控訴警橫行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200104/large/1578068361_e137.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200104%2Flarge%2F1578068361_e137.gif&h=81ad68ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一幅寫上「魔警橫行亂殺人」的直幡，昨晨被人掛在油塘魔鬼山上，以譴責警方連月來對市民的暴行。直幡長約十五米闊約兩米，以黑底白字呈現。直幡上除寫有譴責警方暴行的字句，更畫有「開槍」的圖案，而魔鬼山對面的油塘屋苑，不乏住有警務人員的紀律部隊宿舍。事後多名消防員登上魔鬼山，然後縋繩而下，將直幡拆走。另昨晨11時，有人在獅子山頂掛青天白日滿地紅旗，事後由消防員拆走。<br />\n<br />\n劉永明攝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635189b0c5f1c4ff3e84799bc37aece02651067c","tid":1811271,"uid":207087,"like":0,"disli